Summary: 7 bright objects ascending upwards into one formation at enormous speed.
divs: Sighting Detailsi was at my summer villa outside the suburb of karaj which is 45km outside of tehranwatching a movie in the garden on my laptop when i saw seven bright objects 3 on one side 4 on the other one flew right over me at a very low altitude and joined the others as the last one of 7 like an upside down V ascendinginto orbit, very surreal it made a very low pitch noise as it flew over head i wouldve expected it to be louder the accelaration was unbelieveble once it started going upwards it was circular in shape generally with no engines that i could see its initial altitude was around 40meters and my villa is around 60-65km outside the capitol and is not densly populated
trends: There have been no other sightings in Karaj
This sighting has never been favorited.
